      <div class="v4-metric"><span class="v4-metric-val">07</span><span class="v4-metric-lbl">DNA rules</span></div>
    </div>

    <!-- DNA rules -->
    <div class="sw2-sep"><span class="sw2-sep-label">The Rules of SWITCH DNA</span></div>
    <div class="v4-rules">
      <div class="v4-rule"><span class="v4-rule-num">01</span><span class="v4-rule-name">Industrial Honesty</span><div class="v4-rule-desc">No fake surfaces. Welds, fasteners, and brackets are the visual system. Nothing is hidden.</div></div>
      <div class="v4-rule"><span class="v4-rule-num">02</span><span class="v4-rule-name">Rectilinear Mass</span><div class="v4-rule-desc">Block geometry. Flat planes. Soft macro radii 25–40mm. The battery sets the anchor.</div></div>
      <div class="v4-rule"><span class="v4-rule-num">03</span><span class="v4-rule-name">Tube Logic</span><div class="v4-rule-desc">26–32mm constant diameter. Mandrel bends. Exposed TIG welds. Never blended.</div></div>
      <div class="v4-rule"><span class="v4-rule-num">04</span><span class="v4-rule-name">45° Chamfers</span><div class="v4-rule-desc">Hard surface transitions only. 3–8mm cuts. Micro-fillet 0.5–1mm. No Class-A surfacing.</div></div>
      <div class="v4-rule"><span class="v4-rule-num">05</span><span class="v4-rule-name">CMF Binary</span><div class="v4-rule-desc">Brushed aluminium + matte black polymer. HV orange on real HV only. No imitation.</div></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Products -->
    <div class="sw2-sep" style="padding-top:48px;"><span class="sw2-sep-label">DNA In the Wild — Products Built on the System</span></div>
